// #taxon[Taxon]
#title[Species of Types]

This is a small attempt at _deformalizing_ the foundational work on *species*
that is present in `agda-unimath` with the goal to be more human-readable.

See
#external("https://unimath.github.io/agda-unimath/species.html")[agda-unimath/species]

